Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:16.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pelmeni? You're making pelmeni, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:47.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:50.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:51.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:55.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really good at stuffing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Hei. You can make the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are these steamed buns?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you blind? It's pelmeni.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A Russian dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:17.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the soup is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The meat buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's pelmeni...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll follow July.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:30.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if they're big?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They taste the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move separately today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:42.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have things you gotta take care of as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:52.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of my own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:59.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of my own problems, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:12.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201 killed Youko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who kidnapped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:18.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:22.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He probably got Izanami's whereabouts out of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Youko knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hazuki and I will take care of this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:34.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You two will find out where Mikhail Pavlichenko's kid is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:39.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving us out of this, despite what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,One of our comrades was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:46.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Outsiders should stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:50.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi looks at the false bottom of the sea, waiting for Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:56.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami will eventually cross it, and those two will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:59.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When they meet, Heaven and Earth will be split asunder,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and the Hell's Gate will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:06.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,From there will come something alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:09.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And conflicts will continue forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:15.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what was written in the classified Mitaka Documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:19.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was told these were the memories of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:27.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If this is true, something terrible will happen when Izanami and Izanagi meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:31.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That sign will become an unsinking crescent moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:37.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then, when it becomes a full moon, it will be Izanami's last month of pregnancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see, you've investigated this thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:43.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As you're concerned, the final phase of the predictions has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:49.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell you about this to avoid unnecessary confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:53.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, one interpretation of this has even led to a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The Heaven's War?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:01.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami's awakening cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:05.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We have only one last measure to prevent that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We have to capture and kill Izanagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:12.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,before he meets Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:17.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He must have gone to see Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:25.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The Yin we knew and the one that's feared as Izanami now have completely different personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:31.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Some people say she evolved, but Hei doesn't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks that he changed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:38.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why he wants to bring an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:41.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have to do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to settle this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:51.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll meet Shion and talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:08.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This place is quite lonely for the last stop of the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:17.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:20.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:22.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't they kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That was a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:30.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just a doll that was created to protect me from bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:33.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:35.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're the same as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a copy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:49.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I met Mama... and heard that I had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:53.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's as irresponsible as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:56.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know anything about me and Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:03.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she told you, but think of it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You are not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:11.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You are standing in front of me, with your feelings and memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:15.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that your body died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But you've been revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Shion's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:20.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't create me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:30.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember how Shion became \Na contractor two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:33.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We were in Siberia that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:39.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,After hunting, we made a fire and drank warm soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:44.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then... Shion became a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a lie too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that a star fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But what happened afterwards is a bit different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:57.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, Shion has been a contractor ever since he was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He was special from the beginning, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:05.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And you were never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion! Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:34.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I was unable to understand what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:38.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,His power is to create copies of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:40.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But he had never copied a human before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let alone, himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:45.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:47.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That's why she is Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:53.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All copies that Shion created had one thing different from the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:57.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly what, but it matters not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Then... what about my memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:04.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have my own memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:11.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's because I used the ME to extract and transfer those memories plus the memories Shion created.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:16.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, only with memories up until you were five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:19.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So the memory of the aquarium...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:24.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's a present from Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:38.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:42.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Papa! Let me see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We've found Professor Pavlichenko's kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Toshimaku, East Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:01.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Toshimaku, East Ikebukuro... and what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone seems to have interfered with our doll system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:10.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:15.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that the dolls were connected to each other, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:24.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Professor Pavlichenko argued that the ME had a similar network structure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you bringing that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it fit the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, let's go to Sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:40.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing the general location is enough for us to figure out the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure my lovely honey is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:53.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:56.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! July!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:04.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything if they've been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:12.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell their doll the escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Good girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:18.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They’ve found out about this place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That Sun Tzu fan is pretty good after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.96,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(99,443)}Episode 11    \NThe bottom of the river dries \Nas the full moon appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:09.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are those legs a reward for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Daddy is with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:17.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this has got to be my lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:18.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Come to daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:23.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of you until they grow some hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:27.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your legs of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:29.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hair doesn't grow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It does, when you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:36.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you are as old as me, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:41.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're a boy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:47.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this moron is the only one who thinks that you're Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:50.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Holy cow! The momonga is talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really that surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Chill!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:07.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Was I the only one who got fooled?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:45.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can only run towards the direction of that weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:15:01.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you won't be able to do anything even if you go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:04.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:08.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! She's not our target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing less than expected from Professor Schroeder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:24.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's unequaled when it comes to creating useless tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:27.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or so I'd like to say, but it lacks power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He told me it would vaporize the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we should get ourselves out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:39.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This place is going to turn into a bloodbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:44.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:51.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that there's no Syndicate, America wants to regain its authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why is America involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They want Izanami and Izanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Aren't they...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:04.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but they see them as some kind of energy resource.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:09.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's leave this place to her and withdraw from this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:12.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's been trained for these kinds of situations...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:15.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,by the Black Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:31.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, my lovely honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's that pervert again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:35.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:39.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:52.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mao, take care of Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:15.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! My lovely honey! Come out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:24.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That makes quite an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My lovely honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:43.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:55.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Phew... now that was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:07.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure some people will get turned on by that moaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:10.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have a fetish for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:17.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:21.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be a naughty kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:31.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck! I can't rub it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You won't die anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with us, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're coming with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:12.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:15.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:21.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy to see you grow up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:25.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Are you satisfied with just that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:28.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm no longer the kid I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:32.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a copy and a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the girl you used to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:42.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You will be always my Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:49.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go of that until Shion says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa? Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I heard a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead. We've to go, Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Every defeated enemy should yield some reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,His memories are valuable for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:30.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a little late, CIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:03.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:21.80,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:21.80,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:32.31,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:32.31,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:41.87,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:41.87,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:48.05,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:48.05,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.80,0:21:53.15,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.80,0:21:53.15,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.78,0:21:57.91,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.78,0:21:57.91,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:21:57.68,0:22:06.56,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:21:57.68,0:22:06.56,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:06.38,0:22:11.65,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:22:06.38,0:22:11.65,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:11.39,0:22:18.60,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:22:11.39,0:22:18.60,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:22:18.23,0:22:26.19,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:22:18.23,0:22:26.19,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:22:26.11,0:22:36.48,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:22:26.11,0:22:36.48,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:45.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected that I'd go to the Gate through this route.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:48.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is Shion Pavlichenko really up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:50.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:54.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And who would they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:22:59.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:04.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:10.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They guided you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:12.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Ricardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:17.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer your lover or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:20.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're as cold as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:22.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,T-The squirrel talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.07,0:23:23.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a momonga, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:26.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And, where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:27.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:30.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:33.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She was here a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:36.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Their feelings have connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:40.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Gate. The place where wishes are granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:44.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But also the place where you lose something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:47.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.85,0:23:49.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:50.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:52.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:55.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:03.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers were just wildly blooming there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:09.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When the Gate of Hell opens, the dreams of the future will flow through.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:12.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The crimson moon is a wish for destruction.
